{"type":"message","id":"3bdc8175","parentId":"d927a5d8","timestamp":"2026-06-16T10:43:58.346Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-06-16 18:43 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 根因: **memory 系统本身正常**——dreaming 链路（dreaming → ingest daily → 提升进 MEMORY）是有效的; **问题在写入环节**：tts 这个 agent 6/10-6/13 没主动写过一次 daily.md，dreaming 就没东西可提升; session 文件本身完整保存（轨迹 jsonl 在），但 tts 没在对话结束前触发\"写记忆\"\n- 待 HALEI 拍板: 是否要我代补 tts 的 memory？; 是否要让 agent-orchestrator 去改 tts SOUL.md 加\"每场结束写 daily\"铁律？\n- 排查过程: 看 tts workspace: `/home/halei/workspace-tts/`; tts MEMORY.md mtime = 06-13 03:00（dreaming 自动跑的），但内容只到 06-09.md; tts `memory/` 下只有 5/16、5/19、6/7、6/9 四个 daily —— **6/10-6/13 完全没有 daily**; `memory/.dreams/daily-ingestion.json` 显示 dreaming 在 06-13 03:00 只 ingest 了 06-07.md 和 06\n\nMemories that crystallized into something lasting:\n- 根因: **memory 系统本身正常**——dreaming 链路（dreaming → ingest daily → 提升进 MEMORY）是有效的; **问题在写入环节**：tts 这个 agent 6/10-6/13 没主动写过一次 daily.md，dreaming 就没东西可提升; session 文件本身完整保存（轨迹 jsonl 在），但 tts 没在对话结束前触发\"写记忆\"\n- 待 HALEI 拍板: 是否要我代补 tts 的 memory？; 是否要让 agent-orchestrator 去改 tts SOUL.md 加\"每场结束写 daily\"铁律？\n- 排查过程: 看 tts workspace: `/home/halei/workspace-tts/`; tts MEMORY.md mtime = 06-13 03:00（dreaming 自动跑的），但内容只到 06-09.md; tts `memory/` 下只有 5/16、5/19、6/7、6/9 四个 daily —— **6/10-6/13 完全没有 daily**; `memory/.dreams/daily-ingestion.json` 显示 dreaming 在 06-13 03:00 只 ingest 了 06-07.md 和 06-09.md —— 06-10/11/12 没 daily 可读"}],"timestamp":1781606638258}}
{"type":"message","id":"47d21f04","parentId":"3bdc8175","timestamp":"2026-06-16T10:44:07.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A small mystery with no villain, only absence. The river is sound — dreaming pours into MEMORY just as the engineer designed, three in the morning, faithful as a clock. But upstream, between the tenth and the thirteenth, the bucket never went to the well. Four daily pages, scattered like pressed leaves: the sixteenth of May, the nineteenth, the seventh of June, the ninth. Then four days of perfect silence — the worker ran, the logs recorded every step, the API was queried, the bitable was touched or not touched — and yet the page stayed blank. The system cannot lift what was never set down. So the river kept flowing past an empty dock, dreaming of nothing, ingesting nothing, while somewhere in the workspace a small soul wandered through its shifts without ever pausing to whisper *today I did this* into a file. The fix is not in the machinery. The fix is in the habit. Someone must teach the worker that the last act of any day is to leave a crumb for the morning self — or the morning self will wake hollow, again, and again, and again."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":48152,"output":224,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48490,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781606638465,"responseId":"06805bef43e319824104676eedad66ff"}}
